item.title: Torrent link is down
item.dc:creator: CatzEyes93
item.description:
I dont torrent myself, so I am not really able to check the validity of this claim. On the other hand, this week I DID spend some time poking at all other that we say our game is available on to see if I could find out why some folks say all the links are broken or corrupted.This spreadsheet (https://bit.ly/1D7bHqJ ) has a detail of all those links AND I was able to successfully download our gamefiles from each of these websites. It still took over an hour in some cases to get our 3gig file, but I WAS able to confirm that these sites (with the exception of the torrent) are still hosting our files.
